MAT	<p>008. 8325</p> <p>Match the following pedigrees to their most likely inheritance type.</p> <p>Note: <i>each inheritance type will only be used ONCE.</i></p> 	<p><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding: 0;
